Package: packer
Title: An Opinionated Framework for Robust use of 'JavaScript' with R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "John",
           family = "Coene",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jcoenep@gmail.com")
Description:
  Enforces good practice and provides convenience functions to make work with JavaScript 
  not just easier but also scalable. It is a robust wrapper for npm and webpack that enables 
  to modularise JavaScript code, leverage npm packages, and much more.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
